# Test fixtures and binary assets must never be line-ending converted.
# The hand-built PDF fixtures are mostly ASCII (no NUL bytes), so without this
# git would treat them as text and CRLF conversion would corrupt byte offsets
# and stream /Length values.
*.pdf binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.mp4 binary
# OOXML packages (ZIP) and the synthetic malformed/encrypted Office fixtures.
*.docx binary
*.xlsx binary
*.pptx binary
*.docm binary
